description: With the record of 0-1 on NK, Trey Turner is back looking for victory. He knows what it takes on NK and he's been working on his cardio. Sebastian Keys defeated his larger opponent in his first match and has a record of 1-0. Sebastian has training in martial arts and he uses it to his full advantage. Sebastian and Trey fight hard for sexual domination.
title: Trey Turner vs Sebastian Keys
